Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大男生合夥來欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙真是差勁  差勁透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊  遠阪  這跟你又沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們也來對我做同樣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不就和我有關係了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須保持平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想操控魔力必須要時刻控制好自己的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果操控有誤  魔力會反噬自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過度的力量與錯誤的方法不僅對自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會給身邊的人帶來危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時刻牢記正確的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是遠阪家的家訓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「時刻保持從容  優雅處事」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到這種事琴音可不能忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果錯在他們的話  你可得發發脾氣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凜真是厲害  敢那麼直接地說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有呢  這是很普通的事情吧  或者說理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  這都是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親  再多教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要怎麼才能做出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  對於現在的凜來說或許有些難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  只要凜你每天努力  總有一天能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說  你可是遠阪家的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小凜  這個地方可不可以教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個在教科書的23頁有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊只是在這裡計算錯誤了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問題嘛…你看  和這個例題是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  凜好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來坐下  我按順序教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要去禪城那邊住才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦聖杯戰爭開始  冬木市就已不算安全之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想幫父親贏得聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜  不能給爸爸添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是累贅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非如此  這次要以比過去更齊全的準備來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中也包含了確保你們的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此凜和媽媽最好還是離開冬木市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也能幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  只是父親還沒有教給我足夠的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我自己學就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完…完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.15,up,NTP,0,0,0,,啟此門者為何許人也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.97,up,NTP,0,0,0,,或可為吾友朋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.85,up,NTP,0,0,0,,執吾之手  以此為誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.48,up,NTP,0,0,0,,相會於吾陋室之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:38.80,up,NTP,0,0,0,,汝之手   是小？是大？是瘦？是硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.15,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Du,  wer die Tür geöffnet hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.97,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,wird  freunde  sein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.85,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Für die Aussage nimm meine Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.48,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,wir  werden  in  meinem  Zimmer  treffen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:38.80,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Sind deine Hände, Klein? Gross? Schlank? Steif?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得把書合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對凜來說  要看這本書還為時過早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界上有些東西自身就帶有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫魔力針
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然平時不會有任何反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果附近有魔術的痕跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜  你用魔力發動它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後對於剛才那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有這種反應的東西是凜還無法應付的  必須小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把這個送給凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算提前送你的生日禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等聖杯戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓你嘗試一下更為正式的寶石魔術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於  異變開始產生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是自習哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上的新聞也是綁架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}最近冬木市經常發生兒童突然失蹤的案件…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師他們一直在開會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天第五節課不上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但老師說得呆在家裡不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是綁架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被綁架的都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體好像沒有放進棺材裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟樣子很淒慘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案件的確是在冬木市發生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是和琴音同班的遠阪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在電話無人接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在聽到「嘀」的一聲後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…夜晚的冬木市？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和白天完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人感覺好不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒見過這樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是說到處都有魔力的痕跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須得找到琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這麼晚了還帶著孩子外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險  要是被發現了肯定會被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  小心點走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩的數量變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要躲起來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去  什麼也做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被下了什麼魔術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？怎麼  迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們正準備開派對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人數還有點不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也來幫幫忙呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  這種事就得人多才熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑什麼跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是用那手鐲  把大家給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:15:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要破壞掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  你還是願意幫忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可沒時間哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下估計要挨老爺罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小凜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了啊  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有這種反應的東西是凜還無法應付的  必須小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜…沒想到竟然會去了冬木市…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凜她沒事  只是睡過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是間桐家的魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以肉體為巢穴  以靈魂為食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這些代價才能換來如此的魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過小櫻會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她變成這樣之前  我一定會將她救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,髒硯想要的只有聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他答應我只要能得到那東西  他便會放了小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說…聖杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Servant是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於現在的小櫻來說  就連抱有希望也是一種折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  請你代替那孩子祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也為了小櫻的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天  我們能回到當初一起在這個公園嬉戲的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候  小凜和小櫻也會重新成為姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  葵  你也不必再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君  你是想死嗎？要和時臣同歸於盡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺禮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放著遠阪時臣的夫人和千金不管  真的妥當麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續監視Berserker的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是小事  但我也確實能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要說這樣就能獨當一面吧  我卻又半途就暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我還不夠成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這也只是現在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有足夠的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天  我會以遠阪的魔術師這個身份開始戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這隨時可能到來的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要勤學苦練  謹記父親的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時只需要將自己所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力又優雅地完成就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有欲望的王者連裝飾品都不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能保護弱者的話  又有什麼意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有任何損失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是固有結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本王要親手殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想要征服世…哇！
